author: AP
title: Mom of T-wolves star Karl-Anthony Towns dies from COVID-19
description: The mother of Minnesota Timberwolves center Karl-Anthony Towns has died due to complications from COVID-19
content:
MINNEAPOLIS (AP) — Jacqueline Cruz-Towns, the mother of Minnesota Timberwolves center Karl-Anthony Towns, died Monday due to complications from COVID-19 after more than a month of fighting the virus.
